<br>
The cleric, however, has to make a certain amount of cash just to keep the group alive.  Those peridots cost money.  If the cleric isn't taken care of, you don't get your buffs.  So after the cleric's costs are taken care of...don't they deserve to make some profit, as well?  They need to buy spells and upgrade gear, too. <br>
<br>
What it boils down to is this.  I want the cleric's cost covered so my ass can be covered in buffs.  Everyone in the group needs to make a profit.  The cleric isn't greedy....they just have to fork out a whole lot of pp to keep us healthy.  <br>
<br>
One last note....If you have never organized one, ask someone what the cost is for one Hate raid.  It's ugly, I tell you, just plain ugly.  <br>
<br>
