title>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 87<br> <font color=#E9D756>(2/20/02 1:09:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3073.topic&index=22>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How much compensation do clerics require?</span><hr size=1> Some clerics buff too much.  WAY too much.<br>
