-Zoldarf <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ulorentic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lorentic</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#E9D756>(2/20/02 1:17:07 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3073.topic&index=23>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How much compensation do clerics require?</span><hr size=1> This is what I know:<br>
<br>
56 levels of a cleric that DOES get compensated for DOTs = Me<br>
<br>
