<br>
Me = Broke most of the time.<br>
<br>
OS is the one of the BEST place for gems.  However, Cleric loot items ( Kunark Cleric Armor? LOL ) are at at much lower ratio than others.  When I go there, what loot am I seeking?  Nada.  Im there to get exp and have fun.  Many melee will move that rbg or css, etc to a twink before spending a weekend in OS.  OS is NBG, as it should be.  But greedy liers abound !  You all know who you are or of someone whom you saw the next day /auct that in EC ...<br>
